{"tid":1329444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非快閃] 由今日開始手足喺自己地區拉Banner「721維園見」","createTime":"2019-07-18T08:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T08:30:09.000Z","uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6693b1a44581fd00dd4a99df5d07da04a76f3cda","tid":1329444,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"記著原則 Be Water<br />\n1. 深藍地區人少唔好送頭。<br />\n2. 見勢色唔對即走。<br />\n3. 最好地區有兩戰線<br />\n   3.1. 自己地區各地鐵站出口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n   3.2. 自己屋苑必經之地 e.g. 天橋, 商場出入口  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">交比地區tg group 儘快 組織</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋記得帶口罩, 即使和平行動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(不建議勇武出席, 因留力721/怕點相)</span><br />\n<br />\n方法有三:<br />\n一、為星期日維園大遊行, 是主要天橋拉橫額。<br />\n二、連儂牆貼海報<br />\n三、是地鐵地面出入口拉橫額。<br />\n<br />\n點解強調拉橫額, 因為預比人搞、預比人趕。<br />\n宣傳嘅信息量只有一句「今個星期日維園見」<br />\n擺街站喺好不智,只需大叫或拉橫額。<br />\n<br />\n請幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33da7987bf80440aa2b686e2d94b815c9ae06145","tid":1329444,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"217a23a111c617c282805ee2232d38a2fa87f12f","tid":1329444,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f232c2fc1ac9d095dcec9e2c29b48e79d22f4691","tid":1329444,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"要打破同溫層"},{"pid":"a5775eb60e251ab2836b96f5c066841de1d7c014","tid":1329444,"uid":1581,"like":0